---
const titles = [
  {
    src: '/assets/identity-thumbs/duelcasters.png',
    kicker: 'Arcane conflict',
    name: 'Duelcasters',
    description: 'Competitive spellcraft, rival personalities, and ceremonial magical combat.',
  },
  {
    src: '/assets/identity-thumbs/realms.png',
    kicker: 'World expansion',
    name: 'Realms',
    description: 'Broader geography, deeper myth, and a much larger universe beyond the duel.',
  },
  {
    src: '/assets/identity-thumbs/spires.png',
    kicker: 'Mythic scale',
    name: 'Spires',
    description: 'Ancient towers, vertical ambition, and the architecture of Spellandrian power.',
  },
];
---

<section id="world" class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-10 pt-24 pb-0">
  <!-- Heading -->
  <div class="mb-8 max-w-3xl">
    <p class="uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-xs font-black" style="color: #f5ce82;">The World of the Game</p>
    <h2 class="mt-3 mb-4 text-[clamp(2.1rem,5vw,4.25rem)] leading-[0.98]">
      Ancient power. Rival orders.<br />Realms shaped by language itself.
    </h2>
    <p>
      Spellandria is built to sell a universe, not just mechanics. The world is ornate, mythic, and theatrical — where every spire, faction, and ancient ruin carries the weight of a civilization that mastered the written word.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Hero lore panel -->
  <div
    class="relative w-full overflow-hidden mb-5"
    style="border-radius: 28px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); min-height: 480px; box-shadow: 0 24px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.45);"
  >
    <img
      src="/assets/generated/spellandria-hero-world.jpg"
      alt="A cinematic view of the Spellandria world"
      class="w-full h-full object-cover object-center absolute inset-0"
      style="min-height: 480px;"
    />
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0"
      style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(8,5,12,0.86) 0%, rgba(8,5,12,0.3) 50%, rgba(8,5,12,0.7) 100%);"
      aria-hidden="true"
    ></div>
    <div class="relative z-10 p-8 md:p-12 max-w-lg">
      <p class="uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-xs font-black mb-3" style="color: #f5ce82;">Lore spotlight</p>
      <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-4">The age of luminous spires</h3>
      <p>
        At the center of Spellandria rise impossible towers, arcane gates, and citadels built around written power. Every region carries its own magical lineage, rival discipline, and buried myth.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Franchise title cards -->
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-5 mb-5">
    {titles.map(t => (
      <article
        class="overflow-hidden"
        style="border-radius: 28px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); background: rgba(14,10,20,0.82); backdrop-filter: blur(18px); box-shadow: 0 24px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.45);"
      >
        <div class="h-56 overflow-hidden">
          <img
            src={t.src}
            alt={`Spellandria ${t.name} identity art`}
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <p class="uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-xs font-black mb-2" style="color: #f5ce82;">{t.kicker}</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl mb-2">{t.name}</h3>
          <p class="text-sm">{t.description}</p>
        </div>
      </article>
    ))}
  </div>

  <!-- Tone panels -->
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-5 mb-0">
    <article
      class="p-8"
      style="border-radius: 28px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); background: rgba(14,10,20,0.82); backdrop-filter: blur(18px);"
    >
      <p class="uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-xs font-black mb-3" style="color: #f5ce82;">Core promise</p>
      <h3 class="text-2xl mb-3">Magic is language made real</h3>
      <p>The emotional hook of the franchise is simple and strong: language is power. Spelling becomes spell-casting. Knowledge becomes force. Expression becomes conflict.</p>
    </article>
    <article
      class="p-8"
      style="border-radius: 28px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); background: rgba(14,10,20,0.82); backdrop-filter: blur(18px); background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 80% 0%, rgba(141,114,255,0.14), transparent 28%);"
    >
      <p class="uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-xs font-black mb-3" style="color: #f5ce82;">Visual tone</p>
      <h3 class="text-2xl mb-3">Mythic, ornate, and serious</h3>
      <p>The visual world leans premium and ceremonial — closer to Warcraft, Warhammer, or prestige fantasy key art than light mobile whimsy. Every asset earns its weight.</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>
